WEBVTT

00:00.200 --> 00:02.440
The Wuzhao and we are mortal enemies

00:02.680 --> 00:04.080
I have no time to deal with him now

00:04.400 --> 00:05.840
Not killing him is already good enough

00:06.520 --> 00:07.200
Tell him to get lost

00:07.360 --> 00:07.960
Yes

00:11.600 --> 00:12.480
A few days later

00:12.640 --> 00:14.760
Qingzhou Army's main force catches up to you

00:14.760 --> 00:17.040
You are forced to fight them

00:17.440 --> 00:18.760
After days of bitter fighting

00:18.760 --> 00:20.360
Still unable to achieve victory

00:20.360 --> 00:22.480
Causing morale to gradually collapse

00:22.680 --> 00:24.680
Many worry the court will later

00:24.680 --> 00:25.960
Settle accounts and execute them

00:26.000 --> 00:27.160
Defect one after another

00:27.160 --> 00:30.320
You unfortunately die tragically in the chaos
